s_Hightower\" title=\"Barris Hightower\">Barris Hightower</a>, Triston's son<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_oldtown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(Aegon%27s_Conquest)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (Aegon&#39;s Conquest)\">Manfred Hightower</a>, Lord during <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Addam_Hightower\" title=\"Addam Hightower\">Addam Hightower</a>, Manfred's son<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Manfred_Hightower_(son_of_Addam)\" title=\"Manfred Hightower (son of Addam)\">Manfred Hightower</a>, Addam's son<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Martyn_Hightower\" title=\"Martyn Hightower\">Martyn Hightower</a>, Manfred's son<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_Hightower\" title=\"Donnel Hightower\">Donnel Hightower</a><sup id=\"cite_re